description: Lists members of an address list.

parameters.name: AddressListId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the address list to list the addresses from.

parameters.name: Filter
parameters.description: Filter to be used to limit the results. AddressPrefix (string) --- Filter to limit the results to addresses having the provided prefix.

nested_params.name: AddressPrefix
nested_params.description: Filter to limit the results to addresses having the provided prefix.

nested_items.name: Address
nested_items.description: The email or domain that constitutes the address.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the address was added to the address list.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If NextToken is returned, there are more results available. The value of NextToken is a unique pagination token for each page. Make the call again using the returned token to retrieve the next page.
